    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and she's been such a joy to own! It\u2019s in really wonderful shape and has been super reliable for all my daily commutes and weekend trips. Everything runs smoothly, it's been well-loved, and the interior is still looking great. It's the perfect fit if you're looking for a solid, dependable car that\u2019s ready to hit the road today. Come take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love how it handles!",
