    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. This example excels in driving dynamics, with the high-revving powerplant delivering linear torque through its individual throttle bodies. Critical preventative maintenance is complete, including a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive VANOS system refresh to ensure timing precision. The factory M Variable Differential Lock provides exceptional lateral grip, while the suspension geometry remains tight and responsive. This is a driver-spec machine that balances analog feedback with legendary M-division performance, perfect for those who value mechanical integrity and chassis balance.",
