      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. Meticulously maintained by its previous owner, the exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine with only minor, expected road wear consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the premium upholstery is supple and free of tears, while every electronic feature\u2014from the crisp infotainment display to the dual-zone climate control\u2014functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, featuring a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine that has been serviced strictly on schedule. Recent maintenance includes a fresh oil change and a comprehensive multi-point inspection, ensuring it is ready for the road immediately. With a non-smoker interior and a documented service history, this car offers the discerning buyer peace of mind and exceptional value.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
