    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next big adventure? I\u2019m selling my car, and it has been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014well-maintained, super dependable, and it still looks great in the driveway! It runs like a charm and is just waiting for someone new to take the wheel. Feel free to reach out with any questions or if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
