    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, equipped with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock, ensuring exceptional mechanical grip. The chassis has been enhanced with a reinforced rear subframe and upgraded bushings to maintain structural rigidity under lateral load. Suspension components remain tight, utilizing the original MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear geometry for telepathic feedback. While the exterior shows honest minor wear, the mechanical vitals are in excellent health, including a recent valve adjustment and rod bearing inspection. A turn-key performance machine for the discerning purist.",
